title: ✿ NICELY UPDATED Lincoln Square 2 bedroom - dishwasher - storage
posting_body: ['SEE VIDEO (copy and paste the YouTube link into your browser):  https://youtu.be/3w6pNDr1sPo', '4549 N. Leavitt, 3rd floor', 'Nicely updated 2 bedroom / 1 bathroom apartment for rent in Lincoln Square!', ' This is a 3rd (top) floor unit in a walk-up building on Leavitt at Wilson.', ' Only a few blocks from both the Damen and the Western brown line stations.', 'Available now!', 'Hardwood floors', 'Quartz kitchen counter tops and stainless steel appliances', 'Dishwasher', 'One queen size bedroom; the 2nd bedroom is small, so this lives like a 1-bedroom + office', 'Radiant heat is included', 'Tenants pay for cooking gas, electric, and a $30/month utility fee for water/trash/sewer', 'No air conditioning - tenants are welcome to bring a/c units', 'Shared coin-operated laundry and storage lockers in the basement', 'Street parking only', 'Cats are welcome with a $100 pet registration fee (per pet) and $25/month pet rent (per pet) - sorry, no dogs', 'Living room 19’ x 12’6”', 'Kitchen 7’7” x 10’2”', 'Bathroom 7’1” x 5’4”', 'Bedroom1 10’ x 7’10”', 'Bedroom2 / office 9’7” x 9’1”', '$350 non-refundable move-in fee per adult tenant (no security deposit)', 'No application fee', 'To see, call or email', 'Heidi Sonnenberg', 'The Square One Team', 'Applications are taken on a first come, first serve basis.', 'To rent this apartment, the following are due up front:', "1)  First month's rent", '2)  Move-in fee(s) and pet fee(s)']
